1) configure docker on jenkins master 
apt install docker.io 
usermod -aG docker jenkins 
service jenkins restart 


2) install plugins on jenkins
docker
docker-commons
docker-pipeline
cloudbees docker build and publish

3) the git repo
https://github.com/vsaini44/maven-hello-world

4) configure the freestyle job for top level maven build 
with pakacge goal and add additional build step to create
 a docker image and publish it on dockerhub
